animeDescription: Official music video for the song Sayonara Freeway by the fictional band Irodorimidori. It is the 39th song in the franchise and focuses on Nanase Hagiwara. Nanase is one of two new band members introduced late last year as a part of the "2nd season" in the franchise's lore.
